<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7968436>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1 Summary tree based on the FULL dataset showing the major clades supported in this study. Colours are the same as in Espeland et al. (2019a). Support for major clades is shown. Interpretation of support values can be found in the legend." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7968436/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7968438>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2 Phylogeny of Euptychia based on the FULL dataset. Interpretation of support values can be found in the legend. The scale bars under the butterfly images equal 1 cm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7968438/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7909399>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3 Phylogeny of the Cyllopsis clade based on the FULL dataset. Interpretation of support values can be found in the legend. The scale bars under the butterfly images equal 1 cm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7909399/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7909411>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8 Phylogeny of the ’Archeuptychia clade’ + Chloreuptychia based on the FULL dataset. Interpretation of support values can be found in the legend. The scale bars under the butterfy images equal 1 cm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7909411/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

